Skull and Bones was established as one of these societies, but it quickly

00:04:41.385 --> 00:04:46.385
distinguished itself by its intense secrecy and the powerful network it

00:04:46.385 --> 00:04:50.976
offered its members, of which there were only 15 new ones every year.

00:04:52.196 --> 00:04:57.088
By focusing on rituals and an elite membership, it cemented its

00:04:57.088 --> 00:05:01.818
reputation as a group that was as mysterious as it was influential.

00:05:02.858 --> 00:05:08.948
And right from the very early days, it was the subject of intrigue and mystery

00:05:08.958 --> 00:05:12.928
for students at the university, students who were not members, of course.

00:05:14.448 --> 00:05:20.528
To quote one book about Yale from 1871, “the mystery now attending its existence

00:05:20.798 --> 00:05:26.458
forms the one great enigma which college gossip never tires of discussing."

