Now, with time, information has come out about people who were members

00:05:39.548 --> 00:05:45.228
of Skull & Bones, and it reads like a who’s-who of America’s elite.

00:05:46.298 --> 00:05:52.338
Rockefellers and Vanderbilts were admitted, as well as three generations of the Bush family.

00:05:53.158 --> 00:05:58.688
Prescott Bush, in the class of 1917, his son George H.W.

