And outside of politics, a list of former members contains powerful and well-known lawyers,

00:06:29.938 --> 00:06:37.868
journalists, financiers, high-powered CEOs, men–and for a long time it was exclusively men–who

00:06:37.868 --> 00:06:44.688
controlled hundreds of billions of dollars, newspapers, political parties or even ran countries.

00:06:45.898 --> 00:06:51.408
This has, as you might imagine, led to a lot of speculation about the

00:06:51.408 --> 00:06:56.258
nature of membership, of what being part of Skull and Bones entails, and

00:06:56.528 --> 00:07:01.618
why such a high proportion of its members go on to positions of importance.

