Or, instead, is it that Skull and Bones selects the most promising students at an

00:07:17.868 --> 00:07:22.658
already highly exclusive university, so these are people who would have gone on

00:07:22.658 --> 00:07:26.958
to fame, wealth and power even if they had never been admitted to Skull and Bones?

00:07:27.798 --> 00:07:32.888
Of course, it is a secret society, and members are required to swear an oath

00:07:32.888 --> 00:07:37.558
of secrecy; it is impossible to know for sure what membership of Skull & Bones

00:07:37.558 --> 00:07:42.048
entails and what is expected of former members after they graduate.

00:07:42.728 --> 00:07:47.688
But we have some clues about what goes on behind closed doors.

